<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GymSphere</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
        }

        .carousel {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 40px auto;
            height: calc(100vh - 100px);
        } 

        .container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: calc(100vh - 100px);
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .about {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px auto;
            width: 80%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .about img {
            width: 40%;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .about .description {
            margin: 50px;
            width: 40%;
            text-align: left;
            text-align : center;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {% include 'client/components/navbar.html.twig' %}
    
    <!-- Carousel -->
    <div id="carouselExampleDark" class="carousel carousel-dark slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="container carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="10000">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/841130/pexels-photo-841130.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" class="d-block w-100" alt="First slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>First slide label</h5>
                    <p>Some representative placeholder content for the first slide.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Add more carousel items here -->
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- About section -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1431282/pexels-photo-1431282.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt="about">
            <div class="description">
                <p>GymSphere is your ultimate destination for all things fitness. Our platform revolutionizes the way you approach gym memberships, offering a diverse selection of gyms tailored to your preferences and location. With GymSphere, you can easily browse through various gyms, comparing features, facilities, and membership plans to find the perfect fit for your fitness journey. But that's not all â€“ GymSphere goes beyond just gym memberships. We empower you to take control of your fitness goals by providing access to a curated selection of experienced coaches and trainers. Whether you're looking to shed some pounds, build muscle, or enhance your athletic performance, our platform connects you with the expertise you need to succeed. Additionally, GymSphere offers a wide range of high-quality fitness products, from supplements to workout gear, ensuring that you have everything you need to elevate your training regimen. With GymSphere, achieving your fitness aspirations has never been more convenient or accessible.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
